October 12, 1959. No. 518, No. 536,

October Term, 1958.

October Term, 1958.

Atlantic Refining Co. et al. v. Public Service Commission of New York et al.; and Tennessee Gas Transmission Co. v. Public Service Commission of New York et al., David K. Kadane and Bertram D. Moll for Long Island Lighting Co., respondent-movant. William C. Braden, Harry S. Littman and Jack Werner for Tennessee Gas Transmission Co., petitioner in No. 536, in opposition.

360 U. S. 378. The motion of Long Island Lighting Company to recall and amend the judgment is denied.
